crs#:#crs_loc_type_qualified_info#:#The training event starts with a test to assess if a training event member already mastered the learning objectives. For all passed learning objectives, users do not have to work through any of the learning content or take more tests. For all not-yet-sufficient learning objectives, cate recommends learning content. The mastery of the remaining learning objectives is tested in an additional test run.
